# These scammers want your passwords for cloud/mail/webmail accounts.
# You'll be asked to check a password, renew your service, or increase a limit.
# And of course, they want your credit card number.
#
# So we have company names from the IT sector here like:
# - Cloud Storage
# - EMail Services
# - Hosting
# - Domains
# - Office
#
# Additionally, we are including AI service providers here.
# The criminals want to renew the subscription.
#
# Real sender names are:
